    • gdt2D

      public void gdt2D​(float[] data, int width, int height, java.lang.String floodChoice, java.lang.String seedChoice, int[] xPts, int[] yPts)
      2D Geodesic distance mapper
      Parameters:
      data - A row major 1D array containing a binarized (0 and 255)3D image
      width - The image width in pixels
      height - The height width in pixels
      floodChoice - A string selecting the region to map; "Map 0" or "Map !0"
      seedChoice - Choices are "LeftEdge","RightEdge","TopEdge","BottomEdge","Point(s)"
      xPts - An array of seedPoint column indices, pass null if not using Point(s) choice
      yPts - An array of seedPoint row indices, pass null if not using Point(s) choice

    • tort3D

      public void tort3D​(float[] data, int width, int height, int depth, java.lang.String floodChoice, java.lang.String seedChoice, int[] xPts, int[] yPts, int[] zPts)
      3D tortuosity map
      Parameters:
      data - A row major 1D array containing a binarized (0 and 255) 3D image
      width - The image width in pixels
      height - The height width in pixels
      depth - The depth or number of slices in the 3D image
      floodChoice - Choices are "Map 0" and "Map !0"
      seedChoice - Choices are "FrontSlice","BackSlice","LeftSlice","RightSlice","TopSlice","BottomSlice","Point(s)"
      xPts - An array of seedPoint column indices, pass null if not using Point(s) choice
      yPts - An array of seedPoint row indices
      zPts - An array of seedPoint slice indices

    • gdt3D

      public void gdt3D​(float[] data, int width, int height, int depth, java.lang.String floodChoice, java.lang.String seedChoice, int[] xPts, int[] yPts, int[] zPts)
      3D Geodesic distance map
      Parameters:
      data - A row major 1D float array containing a segmented (0 and non-0) 3D image
      width - The image width in pixels
      height - The height width in pixels
      depth - The depth or number of slices in the 3D image
      floodChoice - A string selecting the region to map; "Map 0" or "Map !0"
      seedChoice - Choices are "FrontSlice","BackSlice","LeftSlice","RightSlice","TopSlice","BottomSlice","Point(s)"
      xPts - An array of seedPoint column indices, pass null if not using Point(s) choice
      yPts - An array of seedPoint row indices
      zPts - An array of seedPoint slice indices
